  "text": "Adopted Ensemble learners Each of these procedures is followed by a model parameter optimization process and a model evaluation process. The Grid Search algorithm [CITATION_1] was used as the model parameter optimizer and traditional 10-Fold Cross-validation was used to evaluate the model. Prior to the machine learning process, the data was normalized by a Robust scalar, and all of the algorithms used in this section were taken from Python Scikit API [CITATION_2] .",
